name: AxiSki Graphite Black
description:
Axiski Ski-Board Black is unlike a convential sledge, not relying on the use of runners and is therefore is versatile. It can be used in all types of snow, from a light dusting to heavy deep snow. 

You can stand on it, sit on it, lie on it, or even double up and share the experience with the family. Axiski Board is extremely flexible and mould to the terrain you're on giving you more flexibility and allowing you much more freedom when gliding through the snow.

UK DELIVERY ONLY

*We Love Ski Boarding is not affiliated with Axiski Ltd. The Axiski 'stand up position' is Copyright Axiski Ltd.
